# Processed Data
# ==============
# This directory holds processed data on the secure server.
# Path: $NANO_DATA_ROOT/processed/
# See config/paths.yml for full path definitions.
#
# Contents generated by pipeline:
#   ecg/hrv_features/   <- Per-participant HRV feature parquet files
#   ecg/ibi_cleaned/    <- Artifact-corrected IBI time series
#   temperature/        <- Hourly CPTd statistics per participant
#   behavioral_coding/  <- Parsed DataVyu event files
#   feature_matrices/   <- Merged feature matrices per timepoint
